==========================================================================
 - Add the following line to /etc/rc.conf to enable cdrd:

     cdrd_enable="YES"

 - Link (or copy) cdrd.newsyslog.conf to /usr/local/etc/newsyslog.conf.d/
   to take care of log rotation:

     # ln -s %%ETCDIR%%/cdrd.newsyslog.conf \
         %%PREFIX%%/etc/newsyslog.conf.d
==========================================================================
